abstract.text: Get collection items of a user inside a specified folder.

inlineContent.text: Returns the list of item in a specified collection folder of a user.
Basic information about each release is provided, suitable for display in a list. For detailed information, make another API call to fetch the corresponding release.
This endpoint provides pagination parameters and also, requires authentication as an owner of a collection only in case the
, or the collection has been made private by its owner. Otherwise, only public notes fields will be visible.
